title: Worst Date Wednesday: "Rachel I'm Ready"
description: Rachel tells us the story about how she went out with a guy that took her on a really nice date.  To the movies and the out to a nice restaurant and afterwards they were back at her place watching TV when she fell asleep.  What she woke up to was VERY surprising and the whole date took a turn....
